name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForAdultRheumatoidArthritis
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Adult Rheumatoid Arthritis
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to adult rheumatoid arthritis and is listed as a rheumatologic/autoimmune/inflammatory condition on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes adult rheumatoid arthritis, Felty's syndrome, and rheumatoid vasculitis.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes juvenile rheumatoid arthritis.)
